1973;;The Roommates;;American;;Arthur Marks;;Marki Bey, Pat Woodell;;thriller;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Roommates;;Five young women named Beth, Brea, Carla, Heather, and Heather's cousin Paula take their summer vacation together at a resort on Lake Arrowhead, where they go to parties and become involved with local men. However, things go haywire for the women when a mysterious killer targets them.[2]